beer.beer_description:
Pura Vida is a philosophy that encourages the appreciation of life’s simple pleasures: slowing down, celebrating the little things, and refusing to take anything for granted. This creamy pineapple and pink guava sour channels relaxed, island vibes: chill out and enjoy! 

Brewed for Beer Cartel Advent Calendar 2022.

CONTAINS LACTOSE.

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!
